{"tid":865970,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"hea 遊泰國 - 跟💩🐒去曼谷個肺踩單車","createTime":"2018-10-17T13:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T11:05:24.000Z","uid":209651,"like":14,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e3825e50c54094dbd321f8af62cedd64b76b3ebe","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"泰國係其中一個很討喜嘅地方，bkk啲粉紅姣的嘅熱情氛圍，令人忍唔住每年回鄉一次😂<br />\n最近跟💩🐒去左 Pattaya和曼谷，適逢鼻敏感大發作搞到發炎，撞啱落雨又無乜plan, 無去到好多地方，純粹hea 下，比較特別就係去左曼谷個肺踩單車😂<br />\n第一次喺度出簡單遊記，請多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<br />\n喺機場出現，飛機上面睇風景，總係百看不厭☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204312_53b25fda65d34a4f736cfc15a29132ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204312_53b25fda65d34a4f736cfc15a29132ee.png&h=58fa2b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，又係零晨✈️，到曼谷Suvarnabhumi Airport 嘅時間大概四點幾五點，隨便吃啲嘢，兌換泰🐷，就去機場底層最左手邊-芭提雅巴士售票處買飛，華欣同一counter，比預期早有車，六點半就出發💪🏻💪🏻車程算快，瞓一瞓未到九點就到左😂<br />\n<br />\n清晨嘅 Pattaya 天氣幾清爽，就唔太鐘意嗰邊啲路比較唔好行，多車又沙塵滾滾🙈🙈🙈一夜無瞓好，拉住行李走往酒店的路，有啲吃力🙈<br />\n不過見倒呢個路口，就知道酒店不遠了☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204529_9b72c4c6daae2b6dbadb562445855370.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204529_9b72c4c6daae2b6dbadb562445855370.png&h=77a41e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寄存完行李，喺酒店lobby 抖陣，距離check in時間仲好長，就去外面搵食😂<br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<br />\n經過一輪運動，個肚早就扁左怪叫🙊🙊🙊😂由於要留後著，就喺街邊麵檔隊左碗魚丸粉來個小朵頤😂<br />\n<br />\n聞說 Pattaya 有家cafe 嘅泰tea 好很正，上層係厚滑綿密嘅奶泡，配著濃郁茶味，口味雖偏甜，又真係不錯❤️ 明明吃過麵，兩條友痴L線忍唔住嚟多個甜品😂 久違了的「cow了物芒」（迷膠泰文粵音：cow了&mdash;-糯米飯，物芒&mdash;-芒果）<br />\n真係掛死朕😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204743_848a8f78a9756b7b388fff4518b5d91a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204743_848a8f78a9756b7b388fff4518b5d91a.png&h=42edb1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204748_a4a65a8891b1929b2252529e8527461c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204748_a4a65a8891b1929b2252529e8527461c.png&h=66b90598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204754_cbe53919d8413e71d704e74cf86f230f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204754_cbe53919d8413e71d704e74cf86f230f.png&h=4e5b0613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204755_81a1cdd3b13a31de65e4937a1df4d1b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204755_81a1cdd3b13a31de65e4937a1df4d1b0.png&h=e1e52705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐喺窗邊角落，幾享受呢度嘅氣氛☺️比外邊塵土飛揚好多了☺️<br />\n<br />\n喂，呢間堅係正，可以試下☺️<br />\n***Jasmin's Caf&eacute; Pattaya （137 ม.9 ถ.พัทยากลาง ตำบล หนองปรือ Amphoe Bang Lamung, Chang Wat Chon Buri 20150泰國）同蓮姐芒果糯米飯喺同一大街上，幾容易搵，環境不錯☺️"},{"pid":"bbd0b44ad594a8515b028c2ef56683581be79bdd","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"兩條行路撚食飽就周圍行下，本嚟想睇新商場T21 Pattaya, 原來仲未開幕@@ 天氣愈嚟愈悶熱，都無乜影相照，就改道 Central Marina🙈<br />\n要注意Pattaya 的商場都開11點🙈對於奴性極重嘅香港人嚟講好似有啲太晏😂😂😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204945_603e418d3cd1360562957052890239f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204945_603e418d3cd1360562957052890239f2.png&h=5b466e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCentral Marina 的外觀有啲似日韓outlet fu☺️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205020_70b1d6f7528e52d51f23e06127c53190.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205020_70b1d6f7528e52d51f23e06127c53190.png&h=09638c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205135_0446aa5f74060ffdcc8d049c2b30dc09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205135_0446aa5f74060ffdcc8d049c2b30dc09.png&h=f53838b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地方唔算好大，一般大品牌嘅運動舖，雜貨小物和食店都算齊全☺️<br />\n<br />\nyeah~仲見到「好朋友」😂<br />\n自從幾年前去過一次兩個月東南亞之旅，在熱到無朋友嘅老撾永珍街頭遇到&mdash;&mdash;Swensen &lsquo;s ，我地就認定佢係好朋友😂😂😂 坐低一杯冰水，一杯雪糕，簡直係荒漠嘅救星呀頂😂😂😂以後只要見倒呢間嘢，都忍唔住要吔一吔☺️😂<br />\n<br />\n💩🐒要左個榴連大乜袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205229_a795b44ade1f0289cc3729381e256615.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205229_a795b44ade1f0289cc3729381e256615.png&h=33771367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就要左個新嘢rainbow<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205255_bd36ef6075c875af7230143c0ba6ce99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205255_bd36ef6075c875af7230143c0ba6ce99.png&h=d5a0c3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實都係最愛nutty tower ⬇️⬇️⬇️☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205444_2395af920fe4aff14fa3929d75d0432b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205444_2395af920fe4aff14fa3929d75d0432b.png&h=dbabf48a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食過好幾家，無諗過始終係永珍嗰間最好味☺️☺️☺️都可能因為嗰兩月喺東南亞太放浪形骸，所以特別美好😂<br />\n<br />\n喺附近嘅街兜下，真係好鍾意泰國嘅graffiti，尤其係著名的 Alex face☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205637_e0f4d551f0b7580b8e87bd781d109fbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205637_e0f4d551f0b7580b8e87bd781d109fbe.png&h=da8d4ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205641_b6a6a5ca7176bcfbcfdf28ac517a3aa7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205641_b6a6a5ca7176bcfbcfdf28ac517a3aa7.png&h=483b1791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<br />\n行到一點鐘，其實已經好L攰，就先回酒店，好彩俾我們提早拎房☺️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205744_90df1f621caa2195d3fa096756690523.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205744_90df1f621caa2195d3fa096756690523.png&h=491e0699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實對於住宿，我地唔一定要住好正好豪嘅酒店，主要睇性價比，有窗開明乾淨就好，最怕陰深feel@@ 反正就夜晚瞓個覺嘛😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205744_74689f6bdbe439b5f87ac3273da26486.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205744_74689f6bdbe439b5f87ac3273da26486.png&h=b02555c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且呢排無乜好吸引嘅泰國新酒店實，呢家 At Mind Exclusive Pattaya (42/111 หมู่ที่ 9 ถนน พัทยากลาง ซอย 12 Muang Pattaya, Amphoe Bang Lamung, Chang Wat Chon Buri 20150泰國) 包早餐，有小型開放式廚房，洗衣機，廁所浴室空間大，除了露台細啲，泳池唔吸引，都同以前住過嘅清邁、華欣精品酒店或曼谷新酒店不能相提並論，但先至三四百一晚已經無得好講🙊☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205745_02618d79cbd3ef8dd5f0ef35e45665bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205745_02618d79cbd3ef8dd5f0ef35e45665bb.png&h=7768b074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好俾天色呃左, 其實都在au雨🙈🙈🙈<br />\n那種焗熱真係想喱喺冷氣地方唔出嚟🙈🙈<br />\n💩🐒想話今天去埋真理寺，但一睇我個衰樣就打消了😂🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n我真係好需要休息休息先再行倒喇，攰到七個一皮企喺度都瞓得著🤦🏻&zwj;♂️🤦🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/210607_6e2e3faddf3248f946ee2860decef50c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F210607_6e2e3faddf3248f946ee2860decef50c.png&h=8338ac7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明知鼻敏有啲嚴重仲咁搏打嘅款，活該之後發高燒🙈🙊😂😂😂無可否認，咁睇住外邊食最好味嘅利💩魷魚味薯片，真心正😂😂😂"},{"pid":"362561cb6ecbdc05fe5f5f9ce3a5c5115e704be4","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"攤到三點幾又係醫肚子嘅時候，是但喺大街市場上食啲啲，點知兩條粉人又失控🙈😂😂說好的簡單下午茶呢😂😂😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/210716_ee02d0f0fe7ef239f1203115cdf34557.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F210716_ee02d0f0fe7ef239f1203115cdf34557.png&h=ac1ac5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但要講下個燒大頭蝦真係有驚喜，以為普通料又揸流攤，點知一剝蝦頭漏晒汁，新鮮大隻夾彈牙，店員仲識兩句廣東話，超有親切感☺️<br />\n<br />\n沿著海邊散步，看看日落。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/210955_ccce8bb2998ee607425fb2ce69d478a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F210955_ccce8bb2998ee607425fb2ce69d478a3.png&h=e6d537cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/210956_e08ded9dfa1e14bb211ef9de0130056c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F210956_e08ded9dfa1e14bb211ef9de0130056c.png&h=3641363e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/210957_427b49cd69dd4e1f7166c0ac4c0e80e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F210957_427b49cd69dd4e1f7166c0ac4c0e80e6.png&h=e0f88000&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/210958_b71ab6a5324d7ad029b38b3ff75cba16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F210958_b71ab6a5324d7ad029b38b3ff75cba16.png&h=74b2c631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211001_9c3e76d9f1ea7c3cb0278caf70483529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211001_9c3e76d9f1ea7c3cb0278caf70483529.png&h=ee0bbb44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211005_b04e915e77f7e6369923ff7ae7f1939d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211005_b04e915e77f7e6369923ff7ae7f1939d.png&h=bef11e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能無玩水上活動，加上環境有啲污糟，間唔鐘都見倒沙灘有米奇喺度裸跑🙈🙈芭提雅唔係好啱我🙊 <br />\n一直行到walking street嗰邊，夜晚又落大雨，在商場food court 求其食啲嘢就返歸，一條鋼管都無見識到🙈只見沿海灘都一街白髮老外在揀女女@@<br />\n宵夜又落街買左兩份cow了物芒😂😂😂金媽媽vs蓮姐☺️☺️比較左一下，蓮姐嘅椰汁確係比較濃郁美味☺️"},{"pid":"067b35b72b0102cabc371d9667f2cde5415acbe7","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"第二日叫左tuktuk 就直接去真理寺☺️ <br />\n和清萊的黑白廟一樣，都係一座藝術品@@<br />\n仲建築緊嘅真理寺，要帶安全帽先可以進入😂<br />\n入場費收500b算貴，不過全木雕工藝甚有看頭，會諗起吳哥@@<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211314_7497d499788f20b32ceee4e3fa8c9156.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211314_7497d499788f20b32ceee4e3fa8c9156.png&h=8f9be546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211319_aa6ca37a7c844a50f8dadcbe1e4bc978.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211319_aa6ca37a7c844a50f8dadcbe1e4bc978.png&h=5fcb27ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211328_47bf2e303f2aa675d34c5838c8e71b8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211328_47bf2e303f2aa675d34c5838c8e71b8c.png&h=e6c9b397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗰日撞正勁多大陸人嚟朝聖，又係一個位影百九幾張🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211329_ad576dfc91134ebff2d9d06f38417871.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211329_ad576dfc91134ebff2d9d06f38417871.png&h=7f73603c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211331_b45bccffdc660556863d91f09829eead.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211331_b45bccffdc660556863d91f09829eead.png&h=19fa9f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住真係忍唔住要小呢對港男女，大姐大佬喺呢個入口通道樓梯影左好L耐相睇住佢n個pose都算，頂佢肺影完又行落少少拎住個袋左摷右摷，仲斯斯然慢條斯里喺度飲水，唔該醒少少一係上左去/落返嚟先唔好塞住個入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍唔住大聲講左句：到底呢兩條友要企喺度搞幾耐？ 駛唔駛等埋你地互餵完抺埋咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先見倒佢地行上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/211756_c7591f2ae237dadeab281f1afdd53db2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F211756_c7591f2ae237dadeab281f1afdd53db2.png&h=baf10b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - <br />\n<br />\n出返市區食lunch，再逛下影下街相，就坐mini van去曼谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/213135_3bf422ea730bea8bdac96e7cd415df7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F213135_3bf422ea730bea8bdac96e7cd415df7a.png&h=b065f8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/213136_2c75f6d9785d39a780cd904bcc81232d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F213136_2c75f6d9785d39a780cd904bcc81232d.png&h=183646a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/213137_ca90fee33d96ff3252beeeb5841b137b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F213137_ca90fee33d96ff3252beeeb5841b137b.png&h=7afc01e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/213138_69e2525b47d607354a694015446bd9aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F213138_69e2525b47d607354a694015446bd9aa.png&h=73e955bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/213140_5996a67cab21aebe5fa92666a7057b6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F213140_5996a67cab21aebe5fa92666a7057b6e.png&h=81d72709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/213140_e15320fd93c6eb7c8333211db133a589.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F213140_e15320fd93c6eb7c8333211db133a589.png&h=c3f67a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n待續..."},{"pid":"0a60e0e795899a277a457cbe25d14177815ab673","tid":865970,"uid":117911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:44:17.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"acb49741347f8ae3881cd96ae7d82d76f32deeac","tid":865970,"uid":114589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"啲相影得唔錯喎！留名"},{"pid":"9512763f1bba451d7a64e74064f20d527926a217","tid":865970,"uid":34671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bbd0b44ad594a8515b028c2ef56683581be79bdd","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"兩條行路撚食飽就周圍行下，本嚟想睇新商場T21 Pattaya, 原來仲未開幕@@ 天氣愈嚟愈悶熱，都無乜影相照，就改道 Central Marina🙈<br />\n要注意Pattaya 的商場都開11點🙈對於奴性極重嘅香港人嚟講好似有啲太晏😂😂😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204945_603e418d3cd1360562957052890239f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204945_603e418d3cd1360562957052890239f2.png&h=5b466e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCentral Marina 的外觀有啲似日韓outlet fu☺️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205020_70b1d6f7528e52d51f23e06127c53190.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205020_70b1d6f7528e52d51f23e06127c53190.png&h=09638c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205135_0446aa5f74060ffdcc8d049c2b30dc09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205135_0446aa5f74060ffdcc8d049c2b30dc09.png&h=f53838b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地方唔算好大，一般大品牌嘅運動舖，雜貨小物和食店都算齊全☺️<br />\n<br />\nyeah~仲見到「好朋友」😂<br />\n自從幾年前去過一次兩個月東南亞之旅，在熱到無朋友嘅老撾永珍街頭遇到&mdash;&mdash;Swensen &lsquo;s ，我地就認定佢係好朋友😂😂😂 坐低一杯冰水，一杯雪糕，簡直係荒漠嘅救星呀頂😂😂😂以後只要見倒呢間嘢，都忍唔住要吔一吔☺️😂<br />\n<br />\n💩🐒要左個榴連大乜袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205229_a795b44ade1f0289cc3729381e256615.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205229_a795b44ade1f0289cc3729381e256615.png&h=33771367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就要左個新嘢rainbow<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205255_bd36ef6075c875af7230143c0ba6ce99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205255_bd36ef6075c875af7230143c0ba6ce99.png&h=d5a0c3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實都係最愛nutty tower ⬇️⬇️⬇️☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205444_2395af920fe4aff14fa3929d75d0432b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205444_2395af920fe4aff14fa3929d75d0432b.png&h=dbabf48a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食過好幾家，無諗過始終係永珍嗰間最好味☺️☺️☺️都可能因為嗰兩月喺東南亞太放浪形骸，所以特別美好😂<br />\n<br />\n喺附近嘅街兜下，真係好鍾意泰國嘅graffiti，尤其係著名的 Alex face☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205637_e0f4d551f0b7580b8e87bd781d109fbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205637_e0f4d551f0b7580b8e87bd781d109fbe.png&h=da8d4ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205641_b6a6a5ca7176bcfbcfdf28ac517a3aa7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205641_b6a6a5ca7176bcfbcfdf28ac517a3aa7.png&h=483b1791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<br />\n行到一點鐘，其實已經好L攰，就先回酒店，好彩俾我們提早拎房☺️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205744_90df1f621caa2195d3fa096756690523.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205744_90df1f621caa2195d3fa096756690523.png&h=491e0699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實對於住宿，我地唔一定要住好正好豪嘅酒店，主要睇性價比，有窗開明乾淨就好，最怕陰深feel@@ 反正就夜晚瞓個覺嘛😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205744_74689f6bdbe439b5f87ac3273da26486.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205744_74689f6bdbe439b5f87ac3273da26486.png&h=b02555c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且呢排無乜好吸引嘅泰國新酒店實，呢家 At Mind Exclusive Pattaya (42/111 หมู่ที่ 9 ถนน พัทยากลาง ซอย 12 Muang Pattaya, Amphoe Bang Lamung, Chang Wat Chon Buri 20150泰國) 包早餐，有小型開放式廚房，洗衣機，廁所浴室空間大，除了露台細啲，泳池唔吸引，都同以前住過嘅清邁、華欣精品酒店或曼谷新酒店不能相提並論，但先至三四百一晚已經無得好講🙊☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/205745_02618d79cbd3ef8dd5f0ef35e45665bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F205745_02618d79cbd3ef8dd5f0ef35e45665bb.png&h=7768b074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好俾天色呃左, 其實都在au雨🙈🙈🙈<br />\n那種焗熱真係想喱喺冷氣地方唔出嚟🙈🙈<br />\n💩🐒想話今天去埋真理寺，但一睇我個衰樣就打消了😂🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n我真係好需要休息休息先再行倒喇，攰到七個一皮企喺度都瞓得著🤦🏻&zwj;♂️🤦🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/210607_6e2e3faddf3248f946ee2860decef50c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F210607_6e2e3faddf3248f946ee2860decef50c.png&h=8338ac7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明知鼻敏有啲嚴重仲咁搏打嘅款，活該之後發高燒🙈🙊😂😂😂無可否認，咁睇住外邊食最好味嘅利💩魷魚味薯片，真心正😂😂😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"絲打pm我"},{"pid":"ef7201ff332c6a0d0f1e3086a573dbd50c9b841e","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb49741347f8ae3881cd96ae7d82d76f32deeac","tid":865970,"uid":114589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"啲相影得唔錯喎！留名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388fa270e8158298136bcdbda12c7e3e09f667bd","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩條行路撚食飽就周圍行下，本嚟想睇新商場T21 Pattaya, 原來仲未開幕@@ 天氣愈嚟愈悶熱，都無乜影相照，就改道 Central Marina🙈<br />\n要注意Pattaya 的商場都開11點🙈對於奴性極重嘅香港人嚟講好似有啲太晏😂😂😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/204945_603e418d3cd1360562957052890239f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F204945_603e418d3cd1360562957052890239f2.png&h=5b466e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCentral Marina 的外觀有啲似日韓outlet fu☺️<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>絲打pm我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有乜幫倒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我啲低級會員好似無得pm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feaf886de05a4f3ed8fcf86a5b77de6343e51f53","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"返到親切嘅曼谷，第一時間仆去check-in😂<br />\n<br />\n呢間 Prince Theatre Heritage Stay （441/1 Charoengkrung Road (Siwiang), Khwaeng Silom, Khet Bang Rak, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10500泰國）可能叫唔上酒店🙊佢前身係1900年代嘅電影院，保留左原本建築再改裝而成，除左幾間套房，其他大部份都係合宿床位。雖然位置有點隱閉，但周邊舊街道都係食店☺️ 走出大街，斜對面是Robinson 泰國老牌商場，鄰近有Bangkar Bazaar, 幾分鐘就到 BTS 線 Saphan Taksin 站，交通也是方便的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/162112_42ed79f55c891c9b8fa4fc4e2ceaa73b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F162112_42ed79f55c891c9b8fa4fc4e2ceaa73b.png&h=73d2500f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有樣唔好就係呢度無lift，不過職員好主動又快手幫你搬行李上房間💪🏻仲有果汁同爆谷做welcome food😂 <br />\n可能位於小巷同周邊多食市，所以有蚊@@ 房都有提供插電驅蚊，但吸我血忍唔倒唔拍__佢😤<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/162152_888454bd9026f05142fff0e31b9c3e21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F162152_888454bd9026f05142fff0e31b9c3e21.png&h=2d86fbbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下層大堂仰餐飲和open area,有好多關於電影嘅擺設，同介紹呢度歷史，似一個小型博物館。<br />\n<br />\n呢間算係新開酒店，兩晚都係8舊左右☺️"},{"pid":"cf57c80dabb95b9d79c5cee35d1193dbd1ba13d7","tid":865970,"uid":114589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef7201ff332c6a0d0f1e3086a573dbd50c9b841e","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb49741347f8ae3881cd96ae7d82d76f32deeac","tid":865970,"uid":114589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"啲相影得唔錯喎！留名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"11月頭去曼谷，曼哥part寫好啲！巴托！"},{"pid":"38d1a93c75265e85237f35e82885933d5285aae4","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cf57c80dabb95b9d79c5cee35d1193dbd1ba13d7","tid":865970,"uid":114589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef7201ff332c6a0d0f1e3086a573dbd50c9b841e","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb49741347f8ae3881cd96ae7d82d76f32deeac","tid":865970,"uid":114589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"啲相影得唔錯喎！留名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"11月頭去曼谷，曼哥part寫好啲！巴托！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"曼谷嘅話，今次個trip好麻麻，上年嗰轉會好啲，咁啦，你有興趣嘅話，我一邊uqdate, 再講下之前去過啲咩正地方share俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d16727fcdeee839663ad136db5f0480eace5ea","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"休息一陣，就到今日嘅重頭吃貨大戲，去扮貴婦港女😂其實之前一直猶豫去唔去，就抱住先訂再睇情況嘅心態，除左貴，就因為其他時間都full booking，剩返唔上唔落嘅四點半@@<br />\n這也源於之前有隻臭🐒講想嚟次afternoon tea, 點知一去就去左個勁嘢🙊😂由於病病地加埋公事甚煩（唔知以為係高層講緊大生意🙄🙄🙄🙄🙄），我都唔知自己食緊乜🙄<br />\n話說 Mandarin Oriental, Bangkok（48 Oriental Ave, Khwaeng Bang Rak, Khet Bang Rak, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10500泰國）距離今次住的地方十幾分鐘腳程，有130年歷史，充滿文學氣息，我左睇右睇都只係吃貨氣息😂😂😂左右都hapi birthday,生日歌四起😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/185900_58ed161f8779e39f6cc9ee069282b126.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F185900_58ed161f8779e39f6cc9ee069282b126.png&h=009669bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講堅，食完呢個世界級，覺得幾年前香港食過嘅根本係天堂級💪🏻雖然話呢間係獲獎無數嘅勁嘢，但口味呢家嘢真係對人🙈叫左泰式西式各一，都偏甜🙈吹噓之風不可長,可以唔駛試🙊<br />\n<br />\n食完呢個貴婦餐就去左mbk嗰一帶行下，因為嗰邊有個藝術館嘅地方都可以睇下，但係鼻過敏令我上顎發炎，都無咩心情🙈<br />\n臭🐒就決定帶我去之前想試的 cafe 食好西☺️"},{"pid":"abad58b004b563e4d4eaf18dc8ef113f8a64ebe2","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"之前喺ig 見倒有人喺呢間 Vanilla Cafeteria, The EmQuartier (อาคารศูนย์การค้าเอ็มควอเทียร์ (ชั้น 2 693 Sukhumvit Rd, Khlong Toei Nuea, Khet Watthana, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10110泰國) 食可麗餅雪糕朱古力芒果糯米飯，但係👉🏻👈🏻餐牌上面得pancake😫沒有可麗餅😫又無cow了物芒嘅嘢😫😫無乜胃口，是但叫左意粉和炸魷圈🙈食物普普，嘢飲係唔錯嘅，但都係同商場嘅Roast正好多😫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/193629_89be74b22776d62c904463b548a318f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F193629_89be74b22776d62c904463b548a318f5.png&h=2793c5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - <br />\n<br />\n之前同場食過呢間⬇️⬇️⬇️<br />\n***Roast （1 Helix Building B 693 695 Sukhumvit Road แขวงคลองตันเหนือ Khet Watthana, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10110泰國）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/193758_9431e4d5bf63ed70f65b8ed159e712b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F193758_9431e4d5bf63ed70f65b8ed159e712b1.png&h=cdd24e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推薦Roast iced tea, 係荔枝茶嚟，茶味不但濃郁，有果肉，荔枝味徐徐滲出，驚喜😬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/194155_f3bcecb3cde1660f9386403a74ee1430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F194155_f3bcecb3cde1660f9386403a74ee1430.png&h=002e476b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有呢個⬇️⬇️⬇️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/194409_23590e001bae7a856035708376c2b986.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F194409_23590e001bae7a856035708376c2b986.png&h=3bc1742d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔食西柚都覺得好正😚西柚雪芭完全無廁所香精味🙊酸甜剛好☺️極酸的西柚配上榛子朱力，令我完全對西柚甜品改觀😂<br />\n<br />\n記得附近仲有間食海鮮嘅，有其他分店，有興趣都可以search下⬇️⬇️⬇️<br />\nCrab and Claw (7th floor, Helix Building, EmQuartier Mall, Wattana,, ถนน สุขุมวิท, Khwaeng Khlong Tan Nuea, Khet Watthana, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10110泰國)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/194634_319819b5270164fc36b530a0bc0c44ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F194634_319819b5270164fc36b530a0bc0c44ac.png&h=5f202ae9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b267ee06abe9d02e44973dcab3daca4406d3612","tid":865970,"uid":3039,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"D emoji想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a2ce6010c43a5ac51034b4a92da6f0c858b57f","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"返歸時，喺屈人寺買左幾包涼茶粒頂一頂，隊完就倒頭大睡🙈😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/231702_46a311d5dfd5f1b5dbe95fca3632d742.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F231702_46a311d5dfd5f1b5dbe95fca3632d742.png&h=c48424da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後💩🐒買左米🐷蓮王子🐷肉粥俾我做宵夜...食左兩啖頂唔順好迷要瞓🙈<br />\n（話就話米🐷蓮，但每日經過都煲燶粥咁嘅味😂）<br />\n<br />\n***王子戲院豬肉粥（1391 Charoen Krung Rd, Khwaeng Silom, Khet Bang Rak, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10500泰國）<br />\n<br />\n唔知瞓左幾耐，開始高燒熱到醒左，諗住飲啖水隊退燒藥再瞓，醒起仲未刷牙😂<br />\n迷住擠牙膏，擠出嚟嗰下：___，啲牙膏屎色嘅😑<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/231926_20d5844f88530204e4c438b7c62c9eb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F231926_20d5844f88530204e4c438b7c62c9eb6.png&h=96eea55f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為呢間嘢只提供毛巾和皀液，隻💩🐒話：你病左嘛，呢枝草本牙膏特登買俾你用😌😌😌<br />\n<br />\n🙄🙄🙄"},{"pid":"8af25474f73e5be648db724e356d0dbe1ac8c62a","tid":865970,"uid":105400,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"睇左頭兩個回覆，d語氣同emoji 太撚on9 頂唔順，留言負評上一頁"},{"pid":"8abc33166d362540cf5f8bf70fd1f26e80e9da1f","tid":865970,"uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"你有中二病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431a942a5438e6407e95f1b576356ab0f6b4b1af","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"前一晚燒到軟攤攤，朝早無落去食酒店早餐繼續瞓，後尾被💩🐒的左出去附近食早餐🙈<br />\n就住宿附近，有間百年老店新記，坐滿的都係泰國人，得我地兩件異相遊客😂<br />\n泰國中菜，菜單得幾味：燒鴨、叉燒、雲吞。因為無乜胃口，就叫左小份嘅燒鴨麵同八草茶，個茶我剩係飲得出係羅漢果，清清甜甜☺️麵嘅醬料有點過甜，我撈左啲魚露落去，當然跟港式和廣東燒味不能並論，試試無妨☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/232747_f0c8dd607f91d7676e903be398506577.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F232747_f0c8dd607f91d7676e903be398506577.png&h=1ebdcf88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n***新記燒鴨（1415 Charoen Krung Rd, Khwaeng Silom, Khet Bang Rak, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10500泰國）<br />\n<br />\n食完就行去bts, 帶病就來啲簡單嘅行程，行下 Chatuchak weekend market好了☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235242_e2054dbc3345ca18df5c8aa1eaeb8dc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235242_e2054dbc3345ca18df5c8aa1eaeb8dc1.png&h=39a7f3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235245_2d693d8cc123b69e7b034f94e65e0518.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235245_2d693d8cc123b69e7b034f94e65e0518.png&h=cbe96e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235250_36e6e196003dbe00672dca42593ad647.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235250_36e6e196003dbe00672dca42593ad647.png&h=8831a7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235255_558865057f70e2463b3f39cd112369f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235255_558865057f70e2463b3f39cd112369f8.png&h=37de819a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235257_f6c67a07a36e7a5ce78e65f3ff7df801.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235257_f6c67a07a36e7a5ce78e65f3ff7df801.png&h=0699dbaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235302_8a1d6db0094066a1090ce01e8aa8aafb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235302_8a1d6db0094066a1090ce01e8aa8aafb.png&h=7e5e1f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次都話應該唔駛再嚟，每次都係嚟左😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235510_5cfac2898fc4b379d6715a9ad5854893.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235510_5cfac2898fc4b379d6715a9ad5854893.png&h=64d0133f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235512_afea9b9410550c2cbdbabe5c3cde8129.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235512_afea9b9410550c2cbdbabe5c3cde8129.png&h=4d697932&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235517_70fe5e9f2af01976c185c3be15bc0de1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235517_70fe5e9f2af01976c185c3be15bc0de1.png&h=a8408bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235533_465e8faeb3f2a53f8d64a2078db19b0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235533_465e8faeb3f2a53f8d64a2078db19b0f.png&h=31da5c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實嚟呢邊係想去翟道翟後邊一個新開嘅跳蚤市場，穿過古玩街，就見到一座大飛機，搞到軍事基地咁款☺️<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235626_737aa4fa0889af632a795df2eff1cf1c.png[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235626_737aa4fa0889af632a795df2eff1cf1c.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=v7SFhVMdNLZxt93nRRuBXACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=0742653a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235626_737aa4fa0889af632a795df2eff1cf1c.png[/img］</a><br />\nThe Camp Vintage Flea Market (460 Kamphaeng Phet 1 Alley, Khwaeng Chatuchak, Khet Chatuchak, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10900泰國)是一個用飛機軍事，懷舊復古為主題嘅市集，我們去嗰陣時間尚早，店家先準備開舖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/235631_0e3871e9b626ca2626f772517181f723.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F235631_0e3871e9b626ca2626f772517181f723.png&h=d0e05ad3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04f753957cf9667e720677a21851056f31b27a7e","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af25474f73e5be648db724e356d0dbe1ac8c62a","tid":865970,"uid":105400,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"睇左頭兩個回覆，d語氣同emoji 太撚on9 頂唔順，留言負評上一頁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"各人有各人習慣，唔啱睇可以唔睇，多謝留言"},{"pid":"e9ffed8b639b4391b04a29ff4de908656793f2c9","tid":865970,"uid":70255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"巴打d相好立體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ee6b0910f7b56b326433301ee3a86137a5de2d","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:41:23.000Z","msg":"本想留到夜晚睇下有咩好玩好食，但有點悶熱就改去睇一個幾hit嘅書屋☺️<br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - <br />\n<br />\n其實去夜市嘅話，我都係比較鍾意拉差達火車夜市 （Ratchadaphisek Rd, Khwaeng Din Daeng, Khet Din Daeng, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10400泰國）都幾多嘢賣同食，之前喺度食海鮮有超大條烤魚，勁鮮甜☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/000005_06217e63f5b7233c003f663813766c18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F000005_06217e63f5b7233c003f663813766c18.png&h=b32a156e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - <br />\n<br />\nOpen House Co-Living Space 位於Central Embassy 入面，打造得有啲似誠品，但又更豐富些，開始式空間包括左書店，精品，cafe 和餐廳，文青可以來打卡😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/000132_dfac43c5da82279f3b258ea570f65d5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F000132_dfac43c5da82279f3b258ea570f65d5a.png&h=0cb76f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/000137_098faf9582b5013da3538dbad447e2ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F000137_098faf9582b5013da3538dbad447e2ac.png&h=fe0ca1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/000144_3f0e920a490902367493544b05c0d553.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F000144_3f0e920a490902367493544b05c0d553.png&h=68490f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - <br />\n<br />\n仲記得第一次去泰國玩時，去過Central World 嘅Nara Thai Cuisine, 一直念念不忘嗰個椰汁雞湯。事隔數年，喺Central Embassy嘅分店...我失望了🙈🙈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/003508_e68a377614030ece4174ab9151af5408.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F003508_e68a377614030ece4174ab9151af5408.png&h=9309517c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早知道就去食朱進發的咖哩炒蟹🙄<br />\n***朱進發 （762／5 Sukhumvit Rd (Opposite Soi49), 曼谷, Bangkok, 泰国）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/003631_16ca1874f637c078e44f0cd1fd8b398a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F003631_16ca1874f637c078e44f0cd1fd8b398a.png&h=268c5694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無太多遊客，七餸一湯兩白飯，點左六味海鮮才2140 baht, 不得不提「咖喱炒蟹」，蟹係現秤的，鮮甜多肉，咖哩蛋汁似薯片嗰種重口味，拎嚟送飯超美味。<br />\n燒大蝦雖不及大城食倒嘅，但都鮮美彈牙☺️<br />\n炸蟹球，外脆肉嫩，外面無食到過❤️<br />\n第一次吃到苦瓜藤，比皇帝菜好食😚<br />\n那湯酸酸地，混左豬雜，也是美味☺️<br />\n<br />\n或者去食泰東菜都會更開心：Sri Trat Restaurant and Bar (90 Sukhumvit 33 Alley, Khwaeng Khlong Tan Nuea, Khet Watthana, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10110泰國)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/003658_530c9bda2e1b2fa9e0833d706b12562c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F003658_530c9bda2e1b2fa9e0833d706b12562c.png&h=a2f4d273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間啲餸同cocktail 都出名☺️<br />\n侍應姨姨都好細心介紹佢地嘅菜式，值得一試☺️"},{"pid":"8593865d96b12bc58ed62ff92df5bc38d61a43d8","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"晚餐後，忍唔住去Siam paragon 食After you 嘅Mango sticky Rice 同泰tea味嘅 kakigori 來填補空虛😂病都要狠狠食🙊🙊<br />\n裡面真係有cow了物芒☺️☺️☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/012157_b10a8073be0041100edb10ec4f229ea9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F012157_b10a8073be0041100edb10ec4f229ea9.png&h=b832e3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰tea味的其實也很不錯，不過很少聽人提起☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/012225_0df66c15d136b8966051b7ba71dddb97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F012225_0df66c15d136b8966051b7ba71dddb97.png&h=ced89970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日都落雨，一落水又浸了🙈🙈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/012424_22dd01fcb25ab476b024eda86bf20704.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F012424_22dd01fcb25ab476b024eda86bf20704.png&h=68c1e8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/012425_f14f4e89ad95a513e366a791004998a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F012425_f14f4e89ad95a513e366a791004998a6.png&h=555c0ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拿拿林就返去休息☺️"},{"pid":"18f4bbbd52e411288f9490e89f3740ff255eb9fc","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"曼谷最後一個早上，今次假期唔多，花左兩天喺芭提雅，感覺曼谷是不夠😫😫😫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/014129_a2b485963be07b656f060820c7868344.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F014129_a2b485963be07b656f060820c7868344.png&h=3def9eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早就在住宿附近嘅小店搞定☺️住喺舊城區有個好處，就係傳統小店特多☺️呢間係專賣豬手同鴨，好多當地人外賣或者堂食，應該唔會難食得去邊😂<br />\n***鴨肉麵 （263 ถนน ศรีเวียง Khwaeng Silom, Khet Bang Rak, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10500泰國）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/014216_b5d3e75a5e21084ff4d54d8e74cc2f78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F014216_b5d3e75a5e21084ff4d54d8e74cc2f78.png&h=876cca43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/014221_31574042e094cf36a900851c93f1a124.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F014221_31574042e094cf36a900851c93f1a124.png&h=fa66bd07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點左雙拼米粉，100baht，份量好多☺️<br />\n尤其鴨腸超爽口，味道又濃，不得不讚❤️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/014300_231fdfd746d9d2cf9e2d21928e23a74c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F014300_231fdfd746d9d2cf9e2d21928e23a74c.png&h=63d22dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食飽又係散步消化嘅時候😂<br />\n特地想睇巷子裡嘅塗鴉☺️☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/014438_a19ac960b56148dc6d72413ff75f9919.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F014438_a19ac960b56148dc6d72413ff75f9919.png&h=794272f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/014439_a8612651a12b705e01439b5cacf89668.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F014439_a8612651a12b705e01439b5cacf89668.png&h=5c58c7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/014440_543f3d1ed95d0c3f33cde081abb9bb67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F014440_543f3d1ed95d0c3f33cde081abb9bb67.png&h=94f7451e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地點有點隱閉，走過一條橫街小市集，幾乎到盡頭才發現了Alex face☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/015319_ab467a3eb19d403bdab59622330e15a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F015319_ab467a3eb19d403bdab59622330e15a8.png&h=70d2d5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/015320_222e792dc4f1a3665b3a263e7afaace3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F015320_222e792dc4f1a3665b3a263e7afaace3.png&h=7a798e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/015325_60791fc0293959cd5ba57bb371344aa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F015325_60791fc0293959cd5ba57bb371344aa2.png&h=86938b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/015329_f87336863ee476679895810112118354.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F015329_f87336863ee476679895810112118354.png&h=6d0634e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影完返酒店check out, 寄存好行李就出發個曼谷個肺😂☺️"},{"pid":"5b39779646a6440d7e374380109c17c9e0af689f","tid":865970,"uid":209651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:30:43.000Z","msg":"今次去踩單車嘅地方叫 Bang Kachao, 被喻為 &ldquo;Green Lung of Bangkok&rdquo;，同曼谷一河之隔，帶有小島風情充滿寧靜氣息☺️<br />\n我地好懶惰直接跟的士司機講去寺廟Wat Khlong Toey Nok （Wat Klong Toey Nok, 36 Kasem Rat Rd, Khwaeng Khlong Toei, Khet Khlong Toei, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10110泰國), 市中心過去大約二十分鐘。睇網路上講從寺廟大門牌直走，經過一啲攤販，就可以到渡頭Khlong Toei Pier （59/3 Sunthon Kosa Rd, Khwaeng Khlong Toei, Khet Khlong Toei, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10110泰國）買票坐船過河。我地一落車，有個親切嘅姨姨揮手問我地係咪過河，然後就指示我們可以由廟嘅外邊進去，出現眼前嘅係一個簡陋小渡頭，有幾艘小快艇，阿姨話唔駛錢帶我地去@@<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/022808_e3363e3f87f5ea3a0fafcb76a671173a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F022808_e3363e3f87f5ea3a0fafcb76a671173a.png&h=5d742d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/022812_592385cf0b9776a3fb0a2afd604ad6dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F022812_592385cf0b9776a3fb0a2afd604ad6dd.png&h=df1b4282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過幾分鐘嘅水花四濺，好快就靠岸😂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/022839_4bce8a0eafe653ad50ca655a74fa13a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F022839_4bce8a0eafe653ad50ca655a74fa13a5.png&h=560f0e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見倒一個簡單開放式小辦工室 - Pae Jeob Bike Hire （Tambon Bang Kachao, Amphoe Phra Pradaeng, Chang Wat Samut Prakan 10130泰國）<br />\n有個伯伯就出嚟招呼，閒聊幾句，用一張證件抵押日租單車，一位先80baht可以到下晝六點歸還☺️<br />\n伯伯俾左一人一枝冰水和地圖，親切又細心講解幾個景點特色，可以參觀森林公園，寺廟，水上市場等等，可惜我地揀錯日子水上市場無開🙈🙈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/022943_a722cae44090b7f1a9e85697ca085dcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F022943_a722cae44090b7f1a9e85697ca085dcd.png&h=429c42a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/022947_b9b815d59c55db786f4adf4ccc219c06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F022947_b9b815d59c55db786f4adf4ccc219c06.png&h=f3923bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢仲話單車唔駛上鎖，若是迷路了，就隨便找個人問就好☺️"}]}